| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2813 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ddc1d9ed-9b2e-517f-be68-8c01b72b612a"
